Package: blms
Title: Fit Learning Model using Stan
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Desch", , "simon.desch@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `blms` allows to fit several learning models that predict decision data based on previuos decision feedback
    as generalized non-linear (mulit-level) models using 'Stan' via the great `brms` package.
    This is a very first version, so expect things to change.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    brms
Config/testthat/edition: 3
